profile:
UN Cabinetry, located in the heart of Pickering, specializes in all Customized Canadian made Cabinets, Quartz Stone, Granite Stone and Mable Stone countertop for residential and commercial buildings. We have a group of professional 3D home designers, measurers and constructers, committing to deliver the best services to our customers. We provide an extensive variety of accessories from European and North America, Supreme Italian Equipment for fabricated-production, which are stored in our more than 80,000 SQ of warehouse. Therefore, we are confident that we have the capability and experience to build kitchens and bathrooms with different level of complication in a time efficient fashion. Just let us know about your requirements and we will deliver by exceeding your expectations.

Services provided:


-Free Estimate Free 3D Design
-Professional Design Team
-Local Custom Cabinetry
-Stone Countertop Manufactured
-Installation Team
-Spray-Paints
-Excellent After Service


UN Cabinetry
